    location: "Jerusalem", dateline: "Upper Room, Jerusalem",
    headline: "Wind Fills Jerusalem Room — Group Speaks Foreign Languages, Three Thousand Join Movement",
    summary: "One hundred twenty followers of Jesus experienced a rush of wind and fire above their heads. They spoke in languages they had never learned. Three thousand joined that day.",
