    headline: `One Day, One Priest, Two Goats — The Annual Reset for the Entire Nation's Sin`,
    summary: `After the deaths of Aaron's two sons, the LORD told Moses to warn Aaron not to come at just any time into the Most Holy Place behind the curtain — or he would die. God appeared in the cloud above the atonement cover. On one specific day each year, Aaron could enter the Most Holy`,
