    summary: `On Mount Sinai the LORD told Moses to give the Israelites these regulations for when they entered the land. For six years the fields could be sown and vineyards pruned and harvested. But the seventh year was a sabbath of rest for the land — a sabbath to the LORD. Nothing was to b`,
