    headline: `Red Heifer Ashes Mixed Into Water Used to Purify Anyone Who Touches the Dead`,
    summary: `The LORD gave Moses and Aaron a new law: the Israelites were to bring a red heifer without defect or blemish, one that had never been under a yoke. It was to be given to the priest Eleazar, taken outside the camp, and slaughtered in front of him. Eleazar was to sprinkle some of i`,
