    summary: `The daughters of Zelophehad came forward. Their father had died in the wilderness — he had not been among Korah's followers who rebelled against the LORD, but had died for his own sin without leaving any sons. His daughters' names were Mahlah, Noah, Hoglah, Milkah, and Tirzah. Th`,
