    summary: `The Ephraimites were angry with Gideon: why didn't you call us when you went to fight Midian? They argued with him sharply. He calmed them: what have I accomplished compared to you? God gave Oreb and Zeeb, the Midianite leaders, into your hands. Their anger subsided. Gideon and h`,
