    summary: `Abimelek son of Jerub-Baal went to his mother's brothers in Shechem and said to them: which is better for you — to have all seventy of Jerub-Baal's sons rule over you, or just one man? Remember, I am your flesh and blood. His mother's brothers repeated these words to all the citi`,
